{"tid":2441883,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上女朋友屋企食飯，同伯母講我做資產管理","createTime":"2021-03-11T03:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T18:56:45.000Z","uid":239696,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"25368a6ecc4ab10d221640aad870a5aaf97d421c","tid":2441883,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"第一次上女友屋企，都幾好餸，有雞有魚，不過唔知點解無雞脾。食食下問我做盛行，我就話我幫人做資產管理，伯母唔知點解聽到好開心，即刻叫老公叮左兩隻7仔雞脾比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後成餐飯有講有笑，去到臨走果陣<br />\n伯母 ＝ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我 ＝ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯母：呀陳仔唔記得問你邊度番工添<br />\n我：我番天水圍呀<br />\n伯母：幫人管理投資、資產wo？天水圍有呢d公司咩？我唔知既哈哈哈<br />\n我：哦，天水圍嘉湖山莊呀，幫d業主管理佢地資產...<br />\n<br />\n之後伯母就即刻送客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616665cb69a0e9340f6ff3b1e4a29ae388aac6b7","tid":2441883,"uid":134087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"1/10<br />\n因為我住嘉湖"},{"pid":"85db8e2bc0f81124a0c702d46990cb1ce220e6c1","tid":2441883,"uid":8647,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"你兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩用"},{"pid":"c19db9b988cd7f46e1a66180e5e8536478d0d1aa","tid":2441883,"uid":121259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"係咪尋日見到嗰個男朋友做物管Po嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f92d6397f6660e23a2a1ec605fd7a907f150b9","tid":2441883,"uid":393145,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:03:36.000Z"